{
  "text": "In the RQMC setting, we take \u03b7 i = \u03c8(u i ) in (7) and (11), where u 1 , . . . , u N are the first N points of a scrambled (t, d)-sequence. The RQMC versions of VaR and CVaR estimates are in parallel to [CITATION_1] and (11), respectively.",
